{
  "stem": "2996.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was after-- immediately after Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was important to me, and I think it is important from the-- your standpoint.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other thing is, what I would describe as channeling the race relations field.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I created what became known as the Community Relations Conference of Southern California, which was composed of almost 100 member organization-- many of them labor unions, many of them churches.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Individual churches and some of them whole denomination.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For instance, when the riots took place in Watts, it must have been 10, 15 years ago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "30 Years ago.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the riots took place, the Council of Churches of Southern California created an-- a-- an group-- created a body, a committee-- Commission on Church and Race.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what do you think?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a member of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every time I came to that meeting, I would say, here comes the honorary Aryan.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they wanted help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we created the-- we created this thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was useful in many fights, where the fight had to be fought, not on behalf of the Jews, but on behalf of all of those underprivileged, especially blacks and, what we then called Mexicans, now we call Hispanics.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That organization died about four years ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All of its papers and all of its documents are now in the School of-- School of Social Work at USC.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Lot of good files.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Lot of good files.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They also had a-- a sister organization, which was called Community Relations Education Foundation, because we were active politically.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were active politically.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We could be active politically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So if we could get a good-- a sizable amount of money from somebody, we would put it where we are out of politics.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
